The aim of the MPC controller is to maximize the output power by filtering the spectral wavelength to control the module temperature to track the reference value. Because the PV power generation is limited by the natural environment, the input, output and errors are constrained as follows:300nmâ¤Î»UVâ¤430nm,0nmâ¤ÎÎ»UVâ¤130nm262Kâ¤Tmâ¤482K,-100Kâ¤ÎTmâ¤100K\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
